    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, lets get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>medium egg noodles</strong> to a pot and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2027-Step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
