          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2027-Step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the noodles are cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once the pan is hot, add the <strong>turkey mince</strong> with the <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2027-Step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
